    "en": {
      "title": "Notification regarding private bus services",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Private Bus Owners Association of Sri Lanka said that if the fuel for the private buses is made available in a timely manner, the required number of buses will be able to be put into service from next Monday.",
        "Sri Lanka Private Bus Owners Association President Kemunu Wijeratna said this.",
        "In this situation, Kemunu Wijeratne said that only if the fuel distribution takes place in a proper manner, especially from the coming Monday, we will be able to provide smooth transportation facilities to the passengers. (a)"
      ],
